\/dunetrektours.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/12\/WhatsApp-Image-2024-11-30-at-12.58.01-1-240x300.jpeg 240w, https:\/\/dunetrektours.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/12\/WhatsApp-Image-2024-11-30-at-12.58.01-1-768x960.jpeg 768w, https:\/\/dunetrektours.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/12\/WhatsApp-Image-2024-11-30-at-12.58.01-1-360x450.jpeg 360w, https:\/\/dunetrektours.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/12\/WhatsApp-Image-2024-11-30-at-12.58.01-1.jpeg 1024w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 819px) 100vw, 819px\" \/>\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<\/section>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<\/section>\n\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-7cf6ef4 e-flex e-con-boxed e-con e-parent\" data-id=\"7cf6ef4\" data-element_type=\"container\" data-e-type=\"container\" data-settings=\"{&quot;ekit_has_onepagescroll_dot&quot;:&quot;yes&quot;}\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"e-con-inner\">\n\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-e34a70f e-con-full e-flex e-con e-child\" data-id=\"e34a70f\" data-element_type=\"container\" data-e-type=\"container\" data-settings=\"{&quot;ekit_has_onepagescroll_dot&quot;:&quot;yes&quot;}\">\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-1c32229 elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor\" data-id=\"1c32229\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-e-type=\"widget\" data-settings=\"{&quot;ekit_we_effect_on&quot;:&quot;none&quot;}\" data-widget_type=\"text-editor.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<h3>Itinerary<\/h3><p><b style=\"color: var( --e-global-color-text ); text-align: var(--text-align);\">Day 1: Marrakech \u2013 Imlil \u2013 Toubkal Base Camp<\/b><\/p><p>Morning Transfer: Start your journey with a scenic drive from Marrakech to Imlil, a picturesque Berber village and the gateway to the Toubkal region.<\/p><p>Meet Your Team: Meet your experienced guide and muleteers who will accompany you throughout the trek.<\/p><p>Hike to Base Camp: Begin your trek, passing through walnut groves, terraced fields, and traditional Berber villages. Enjoy a picnic lunch along the way.<\/p><p>Overnight Stay: Reach Toubkal Base Camp and spend the night in a mountain refuge. Dinner is served at the refuge, giving you the energy needed for the next day\u2019s ascent.<\/p><p>&#8212;<\/p><p><b>Day 2: Summit Day<\/b><\/p><p>Early Start: Start your climb in the pre-dawn hours to catch the sunrise from the summit.<\/p><p>Reach the Peak: Upon reaching the summit of Mount Toubkal, you\u2019ll be rewarded with stunning 360-degree views of the Atlas Mountains, Berber villages, and even the Sahara Desert in the distance.<\/p><p>Return to Base Camp: Descend back to the base camp for a well-deserved rest and hearty meal.<\/p><p>&#8212;<\/p><p><b>Day 3: Explore the Surrounding Valleys<\/b><\/p><p>Discover Berber Villages: Take a guided trek through the nearby Azzaden Valley or Mizane Valley, exploring the beauty of the Atlas Mountains and the traditional way of life in Berber communities.<\/p><p>Cultural Insights: Learn about Berber customs, visit local homes, and enjoy a traditional lunch.<\/p><p>Overnight Stay: Return to Imlil and relax in a cozy Berber guesthouse.<\/p><p>&#8212;<\/p><p><b>Day 4: Imlil \u2013 Marrakech<\/b><\/p><p>Morning Walk: Enjoy a short walk around Imlil to soak in the mountain scenery one last time.<\/p><p>Return to Marrakech: Drive back to Marrakech, arriving in the afternoon with unforgettable memories of your Toubkal adventure.<\/p><p>&#8212;<\/p><p><b>Highlights of the Trip<\/b><\/p><p>Summit the highest peak in North Africa.<\/p><p>Stay in mountain refuges and traditional Berber guesthouses.<\/p><p>Explore the stunning Atlas Mountains and picturesque valleys.<\/p><p>Learn about Berber culture and enjoy authentic Moroccan cuisine.<\/p><p>Guided trek tailored to your pace and experience level.<\/p><p>&#8212;<\/p><p>This 4-day Toubkal trek is the perfect blend of adventure and cultural immersion, offering breathtaking views and a deep connection to Morocco\u2019s mountainous landscapes and traditions.<\/p><p>\u00a0<\/p><p>\u00a0<\/p>\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"<p>Toubkal trek \u200b Experience the adventure of a lifetime with a 4-day trek to Mount Toubkal, the highest peak in North Africa at 4,167 meters (13,671 feet). This journey combines stunning landscapes, physical challenge, and the warm hospitality of the Berber people. Perfect for adventure seekers and nature lovers, this trek offers a deep dive [&hellip;]<\/p>\n","protected":false},"author":5,"featured_media":11305,"parent":11315,"menu_order":0,"comment_status":"closed","ping_status":"closed","template":"","meta":{"_monsterinsights_skip_tracking":false,"_monsterinsights_sitenote_active":false,"_monsterinsights_sitenote_note":"","_monsterinsights_sitenote_category":0,"footnotes":""},"class_list":["post-11476","page","type-page","status-publish","has-post-thumbnail","hentry"],"_links":{"self":[{"href":"https:\/\/dunetrektours.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/pages\/11476","targetHints":{"allow":["GET"]}}],"collection":[{"href":"https:\/\/dunetrektours.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/pages"}],"about":[{"href":"https:\/\/dunetrektours.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/types\/page"}],"author":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/dunetrektours.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/users\/5"}],"replies":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/dunetrektours.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/comments?post=11476"}],"version-history":[{"count":93,"href":"https:\/\/dunetrektours.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/pages\/11476\/revisions"}],"predecessor-version":[{"id":12758,"href":"https:\/\/dunetrektours.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/pages\/11476\/revisions\/12758"}],"up":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/dunetrektours.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/pages\/11315"}],"wp:featuredmedia":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/dunetrektours.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/media\/11305"}],"wp:attachment":[{"href":"https:\/\/dunetrektours.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/media?parent=11476"}],"curies":[{"name":"wp","href":"https:\/\/api.w.org\/{rel}","templated":true}]}}